OL,3,CTop island lawyer pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cassaulting a taxi driver
OL,6,FA Jersey-based lawyer who regularly
OL,7,Fdefends people in the Royal Court
OL,8,Fattacked a taxi driver whilst drunk,
OL,9,Fleaving him afraid to carry out his
OL,10,Fdaily job.
OL,12,FDavid Steenson pleaded guilty to
OL,13,Fassaulting a taxi driver while drunk
OL,14,Fat Jersey's Magistrates Court on
OL,15,FTuesday 17 December 2024.
OL,17,FThe prosecution told the court that
OL,18,Fthe victim picked up Steenson and took
OL,19,Fhim to Corbiere on 13 November 2024.
