OL,6,FThe taxi driver then asked the
OL,7,Fdefendant to pay a fare of #35.55 and
OL,8,Fwaited five minutes, but no payment
OL,9,Fwas made.
OL,11,FDuring this time, Steenson then
OL,12,Fproceeded to physically assault the
OL,13,Ftaxi driver, with dash cam footage
OL,14,Fshowing the defendant hitting and
OL,15,Fgrabbing the victim.
OL,17,FSteenson also grabbed the steering
OL,18,Fwheel while the vehicle was in motion.
