OL,4,Cassaulting a taxi driver
OL,6,FEmergency services were called, with
OL,7,Fthe defendant striking the taxi driver
OL,8,Fseveral times.
OL,10,FThe prosecution told the court the
OL,11,Fvictim is now afraid to carry out his
OL,12,Fdaily job and is wary of who he now
OL,13,Fpicks up.
OL,15,FSteenson must now complete 130 hours
OL,16,Fof community service for the offence
OL,17,Fand pay out #2,419.55 in compensation
OL,18,Fto his victim.
