OL,3,CTop island lawyer pleads guilty to
OL,4,Cassaulting a taxi driver
OL,6,FArriving at the court in the morning,
OL,7,FSteenson's defence lawyer - Paul
OL,8,FNicholls - addressed the press saying
OL,9,F"Cover some real news" and "pathetic".
OL,11,FMr Nicholls told the court that
OL,12,FSteenson is "of exemplary character".
OL,14,FThe defence said that Steenson
OL,15,Faccepted full responsibility for the
OL,16,Fassault and is "genuinely remorseful"
OL,17,Ffor his actions.
OL,19,FMr Nicholls also added that Steenson
OL,20,Fwas claustrophobic which may have
OL,21,Fcontributed to his actions.
