OL,6,FDavid Steenson is a Partner at a legal
OL,7,Ffirm in the island but is currently
OL,8,Fnot practising.
OL,10,FWhile he can still practice law, the
OL,11,FJersey Law Society will handle a
OL,12,Fdisciplinary process to decide if any
OL,13,Ffurther action against him will be
OL,14,Ftaken.
